now the energy is just sufficient to heat 
that tungsten plate to bright red. But—"

1549
02:31:52,479 --> 02:31:57,359
Kendall turned over a small rheostat 
control—and abruptly the eighteen-inch  

1550
02:31:57,359 --> 02:32:02,960
diameter spot on the tungsten-beryllium plate 
began contracting; it contracted till it  

1551
02:32:02,960 --> 02:32:09,840
was a blazing, sparkling spot of molten 
incandescence less than an inch across!

1552
02:32:10,880 --> 02:32:16,480
"That's the advantage of focus. At this distance 
of a few hundred feet with a small beam I can  

1553
02:32:16,479 --> 02:32:22,479
do that. With a twenty-foot beam, I can get a 
two-foot spot at a distance of nearly ten miles!  

1554
02:32:23,200 --> 02:32:28,000
That means that the receiving end will have the 
pleasure of handling one hundred times the energy  

