1556
02:32:34,720 --> 02:32:38,560
The trouble being, if it's out of 
focus the advantage is more than lost.  

1557
02:32:39,600 --> 02:32:43,360
So if there's any question about getting 
the focus, we'll get along without it."

1558
02:32:44,880 --> 02:32:48,640
"A real help, if you do. That 
would punch a hole before the  

1559
02:32:48,640 --> 02:32:50,560
Stranger ship could turn away as they do now."

1560
02:32:51,600 --> 02:32:57,201
Kendall nodded. "That's what I was after. 
It is mainly for the forts, though. We'll  

1561
02:32:57,200 --> 02:33:02,960
