Deenmor stations. They can fix it up, themselves.  

1562
02:33:02,960 --> 02:33:08,720
In the meantime—all we can do is hold on and hunt, 
and let's hope better than the Strangers do."

1563
02:33:26,240 --> 02:33:31,439
Sadly the convalescent Gresth Gkae 
listened to the reports of his lieutenants.  

1564
02:33:32,399 --> 02:33:38,319
More and more disgraced he felt as he realized how 
badly he had blundered in reporting the people of  

1565
02:33:38,319 --> 02:33:44,399
this system unable to cope with the attackers' 
weapons. Gresth Gkae looked up at his old friend  

1566
02:33:44,399 --> 02:33:53,280
and physician, Merth Skahl. He shook his head 
slowly. "I'm afraid, Merth Skahl. I am afraid.  

1567
02:33:53,840 --> 02:33:59,280
We have, perhaps, made a mistake. The better 
and the stronger alone should rule. Aye,  

1568
02:33:59,920 --> 02:34:06,000
