we have mistaken the Truth in assuming this.  

1569
02:34:06,800 --> 02:34:11,440
If we have—then may Jarth, Lord 
of Truth and Wisdom punish us.  

1570
02:34:12,160 --> 02:34:17,760
Mighty Jarth, if I have mistaken in following 
my judgments, it is not from disobedience,  

1571
