that these people might learn—and destroy us?  

1584
02:35:44,080 --> 02:35:50,800
If they be the stronger, and the better—then 
may Jarth's will be done. But we must test our  

1585
02:35:50,800 --> 02:35:56,560
strength to the utmost. I must rise, and go 
to my laboratory soon. They have set it up?"

1586
02:35:57,600 --> 02:36:02,241
"Aye, they have, Gresth Gkae. But 
remember, the weak and the sick make  

1587
02:36:02,240 --> 02:36:07,439
faults the strong and the well do not. 
Better that you rest yourself. There is  

1588
02:36:07,439 --> 02:36:11,759
little you can do while your body seeks 
to recover from these terrible burns."

1589
02:36:12,880 --> 02:36:16,400
"You are wrong, my friend, wrong. Don't you  

1590
02:36:16,399 --> 02:36:22,559
see that my mind is clear—that it is the 
mind which must fight in these battles,  

1591
02:36:22,560 --> 02:36:26,640
for surely the man is weak against 
such things as this infra-X-radiation?  

1592
02:36:27,439 --> 02:36:32,799
Why, I am better able to fight now than are 
you, for I am a trained fighter of the mind,  

1593
02:36:32,800 --> 02:36:39,600
while you are a trained healer of the body. These 
strange beings with their stiff arms and legs,  

1594
02:36:39,600 --> 02:36:47,360
