the riddle of the crumbling field. That took us  

1596
02:36:53,439 --> 02:37:00,639
longer, and we designed it. The Counsel of Worlds 
put me in command, let me up, Skahl, I must work."

1597
02:37:01,600 --> 02:37:08,161
Concerned, the physician looked down 
at him. Finally he spoke again. "No,  

1598
02:37:08,160 --> 02:37:13,840
I will not permit you to leave the hospital-ship. 
You must stay here, but if, as you have said,  

1599
02:37:14,399 --> 02:37:20,080
the mind is what must fight, then surely you can 
fight well from here, for your mind is here."

1600
02:37:21,200 --> 02:37:27,760
"No, I cannot, and you well know it. I may 
shorten my life, but what matter. 'Death is  

1601
02:37:27,760 --> 02:37:33,840
the end toward which the chemical reaction, Life, 
tends,'" quoted the scientist. "You know I have  

1602
02:37:33,840 --> 02:37:39,440
left my children—my immortality is assured 
through them. I can afford to die in peace,  

1603
02:37:39,439 --> 02:37:47,359
