hours rest in every fifteen, and a good sleep 
of at least twenty-seven hours every "night."  

1607
02:38:09,920 --> 02:38:14,000
Gresth Gkae agreed, and from a 
wheelchair, conducted his work,  

1608
02:38:14,000 --> 02:38:18,720
