02:38:33,600 --> 02:38:40,161
gaining strength very, very slowly, taken away 
despondent at the end of his forty hours of work.

1612
02:38:41,200 --> 02:38:44,319
A dozen expeditions were sent to Jupiter's poles  

1613
02:38:44,319 --> 02:38:49,200
