Skahl spent with him, calming him to sleep.

1621
02:39:34,399 --> 02:39:39,280
"But what is this constant search? It 
is little enough I know of science,  

1622
02:39:39,280 --> 02:39:44,319
but why do you send our men to these spots of 
wonderfully beautiful, but useless natural forces.  

1623
02:39:44,960 --> 02:39:48,640
Can we somehow, do you think, turn them 
against the people of these worlds?"

1624
02:39:49,920 --> 02:39:57,359
Softly the old Miran smiled. "Yes, you 
might say so. For look, it is the strange  

1625
02:39:57,359 --> 02:40:03,599
balls of electric force I want to know about. 
Sthor had few, but occasionally we saw them.  

1626
02:40:04,319 --> 02:40:09,759
