want to know their secret, for I am sure  

1627
02:40:09,760 --> 02:40:15,280
they are balls of electric forces not vastly 
dissimilar from the nucleus of the atom.  

1628
02:40:16,240 --> 02:40:21,279
Always we have known that no system of 
purely electrical forces could remain stable.  

1629
02:40:22,160 --> 02:40:28,960
Yet these strange balls of energy do. 
How is it? I am sure it will be of vast  

1630
