these electric balls of energy, can I not hope 
to make similar magnetic balls of energy?"

1633
02:40:49,040 --> 02:40:53,920
"Yes, I see—that would seem true. But 
what benefit would you derive from that?  

1634
02:40:54,640 --> 02:40:57,760
