forts. How then would these benefit you?"

1636
02:41:02,960 --> 02:41:09,840
"We can do nothing to those forts, because of 
that magnetic shield. Could we once break it down,  

1637
02:41:09,840 --> 02:41:16,400
then the fort is helpless, and one or two small 
