1647
02:42:13,040 --> 02:42:21,120
He turned a sad, downcast face to his friend. 
"But Merth Skahl, we can't do it," he complained.

1648
02:42:22,399 --> 02:42:26,080
"Ah—now I can see why you so want to continue this  

1649
02:42:26,080 --> 02:42:32,399
