first hint that will lead you to success."

1651
02:42:38,800 --> 02:42:42,960
"Ah—I only hope it, Merth Skahl, I only hope it."

1652
02:42:45,040 --> 02:42:51,920
But it was the next day that they saw the first 
glimpse of the secret, and saw the path that might  

1653
02:42:51,920 --> 02:42:57,760
